23 May 2017The African National Congress has noted the public statement following the Special Central Executive Committee (SCEC) of the Congress of South African Trade Unions (COSATU) "that President Jacob Zuma will no longer be welcomed to address COSATU activities".The ANC has not received any formal communication in this regard, we therefore, won't make any comments until such time there is an engagement with COSATU.Issued by the African National CongressEnquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National SpokespersonKhusela Sangoni 072 854 5707 National Communications Manager